"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"ARK发布了2022年比特币的链上数据评估框架。总体看法：\\n\\n* 比特币目前处在共识加强的趋势中，中长期价格不会大跌。\\n\\n![被摧毁时间下降意味着交易意愿下降，持有共识增强](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5MXPWnhbKCrxwTnEEkxc1.png?height=537&width=1348)\\n\\n1. \\n2. 目前价格处在上涨的区间，但短期是否会向上还需要观察。\\n\\n![短期与长期实现价值比率目前仍在上涨区间](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ng6oQAk3wOx0uRC2zSzjd.png?height=587&width=1321)\\n\\n比特币目前的共识是在价值储存，价格影响最大的因素是传统资金的进入。场内资金都去追逐更高效率、更有创新的“生产性”项目。而2022年美联储有加息预期，这将会是中期（3-6个月）抑制传统资金进入的因素。\",\"timestamp\":1641186312,\"title\":\"ARK 2022年比特币数据分析小结\"},\"digest\":\"u17z42n6BEVK5pgh6iPvEU0Cns54x_QcsDV8_CiaZQY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x130E5d91E578BBdb981362D94A8ed3BBcBbC1Eb3\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DXK1O2Uu-0NJSgiI7pzYZhqyeu4s_WvDAHJAlYSI8oo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IR_Jz1nSYWeghGJJnbffIkVahANFsvNc7pXNqOQMtb0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"G5Yx-raGOhFwZgAE3xe6YCL5yDUN9Jv5_zEmH2mSoovgax6RwX8b8VJ3hjCexhgslgX6yL5I4o06NBxivqqCvA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xdba4e3436986a7e15d6e149ab56b6ff30f848e77cfe9b26fb2cc25fa37d3331a2cff26f1a59949df1e1fcb38da0ce9aa7e26fad04bb99bbfabe249e1e5eabd6f1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DXK1O2Uu-0NJSgiI7pzYZhqyeu4s_WvDAHJAlYSI8oo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IR_Jz1nSYWeghGJJnbffIkVahANFsvNc7pXNqOQMtb0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"u17z42n6BEVK5pgh6iPvEU0Cns54x_QcsDV8_CiaZQY\"}"